Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.68,0:00:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.79,0:00:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.66,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:00:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.99,0:01:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.09,0:01:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.10,0:01:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.39,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是...那個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.77,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.22,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 因為現在有叔叔陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.29,0:03:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第五話沒有笑容的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是前些日子來襲的\N外星異種碎片分析影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由相當複雜的分子程序\N所構成的重金屬化合物集合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.28,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以構造來講\N跟甲殼質的蟲類很類似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其硬度卻超過鑽石硬度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更令人驚訝的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它具備了奈米【毫微】程度\N的修復程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.65,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有自我保存、修復\N以及解體的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼結論\N牠到底是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個物質是一種\N擁有生命力的金屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請過目一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相同的物質\N在七天內的變化影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與時間一起產生化學變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分解成無害的有機物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.51,0:04:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結論就是\N"善待大地的宇宙怪物"是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個怪物!外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止活動之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.79,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會變成生態系統的一環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是被誰\N植入了化學程式一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被植入程式?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是說外星異種\N是由某人引進地球的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說，這也只是一種假設
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.28,0:04:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣的機械生命體\N很難讓人相信是由自然產生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為科學家的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是為了研究這個物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使花上一個世紀\N也解不開謎團吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.76,0:05:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對第一次見面的對手互贈禮物\N似乎是宇宙共通的禮貌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢~還真希望某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以多磨練磨練送禮的禮節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告一下關於\N克萊茵．桑德曼的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.48,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然下令軍方以及\N各行政機關進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其身分、年齡、經歷\N全部不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然擁有各種公司企業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其本人完全沒有浮出檯面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資產規模也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.46,0:05:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現階段\N只知道是個天文數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊茵．桑德曼~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個比外星異種\N還令人感到好奇的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦!英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要浸泡到肩膀才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的!現在還有人泡澡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是桑德曼的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說不可以\N什麼事情都依靠機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是從小就\N跟那個傢伙一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.13,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從來都不覺得\N他有什麼地方怪怪的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~沒想過耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉~從來沒有出過這座城\N跟你講也是白搭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡是一種美學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.91,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是溫水淋浴或超音波消毒\N都無法感受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人與熱水的交流就在此刻!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼 你在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要你回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做莉露的女生又是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把綾香藏到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把小毛巾泡進湯池裡\N是違反泡湯禮儀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別轉移話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!別走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.72,0:07:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我為您更衣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!別鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亂動啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡~又被他跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜，使用超重龍捲風拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?~嗯~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在!愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重龍捲風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然\N這個技術的難度還是太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:08:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...真是很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥?野餐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.64,0:08:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對!想說可以增進彼此情感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像蠻有趣的耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧? 對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小鬼要遠足啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜 妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜是在擔心莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訓練時也不會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不曾說過\N關於自己的任何事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果一起去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以稍微\N打開她的心防才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜人真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪~沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳不是只會耍潑辣而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~天氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫您拿行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不過就是這些而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼就不跟我說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.69,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳猜輸 是英司自己活該倒楣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶而到外面走走也很不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.71,0:09:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風景真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜\N真虧妳找得到這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候曾經來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸曾經在這座城裡工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.09,0:09:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經帶我來過一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.63,0:09:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的爸爸呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的家人都是作什麼的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想更了解妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話，可以告訴我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要、要點火了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.07,0:10:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我\N做錯什麼事情了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.64,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是G呼號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外星異種?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得把莉露找回來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定目標!各機開始攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!都已經正中目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.02,0:11:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡~用我們的裝備\N打不贏牠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種出現在\N中央山麓工業地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,市民的避難措施已順利完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在EFA正在作戰中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是似乎一點用都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 她到底在介意什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在害怕什麼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為讓那樣的女孩\N上戰場的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她笑起來是那麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:11:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了...我的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有記憶了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記不得當時的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只知道眼前一片火海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有某人在吶喊著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也失去了雙親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽以前一直臥病在床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爸爸在桑德曼城工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到了來自\N土星的觀測基地的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說外星異種已經接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此展開調查之後\N就這樣音訊全無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後的聯絡訊息是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.37,0:13:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現外星異種\N立刻就迎敵戰鬥位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.27,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此桑德曼知道了\N外星異種接近的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.01,0:13:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要跟外星異種作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是爸爸的最後遺言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得爸爸\N應該會很高興我這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.66,0:13:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙也是自幼失去雙親\N在這座城堡中被撫養長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司也擔心著\N失去蹤影的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是失去重要親人的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.67,0:14:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想我可以理解妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家都想跟妳好好相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像琉菜說的那樣，莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在擔心妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.79,0:14:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要的話\N隨時都可以告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼好怕的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影裝甲很厚 妳放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在那裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露，外星異種出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要迎戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很了不起喔!莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文，可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個機動兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員究竟是怎樣的傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.71,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.65,0:15:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.55,0:15:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.77,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種以攝氏一萬兩千度\N的熱光作為武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一萬兩千度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是太陽表面溫度的兩倍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.51,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，快點解決牠!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影座艙\N超重新月鏢，發射預備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.06,0:16:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銅製品工廠引發大火!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.18,0:16:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在燃燒的應該是硫酸銅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色火焰... 糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點用超重新月鏢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露，振作點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.13,0:17:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜，可以從外部操控嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處於發射動作當中\N呈鎖定狀態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過去她那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 讓我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜 別掉下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心!我又不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.79,0:18:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 已經沒什麼好怕的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了打倒外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不要再讓更多的人傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜還不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離重力子臨界狀態\N還有3433點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露 大家都會保護著妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 再一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.81,0:19:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.33,0:19:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 最後讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種整個爆開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.38,0:19:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作後來一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是~痛快得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來挺樂的嘛 媚月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有兩個年輕小夥子陪伴嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.25,0:20:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚..媚月小姐\N還是別喝太多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳偶爾也來喝一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是對這些小子們畢恭畢敬\N也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在盡女僕應該盡的義務\N(斗牙 過來這邊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.96,0:20:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 侍奉主人是女僕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.93,0:20:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您這是在做什麼呀 媚月小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 她笑起來很可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?你講什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.28,0:20:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說女人還是溫柔點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.09,0:21:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~你這是在諷刺我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦!我是對這個\N兇巴巴的女人說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還講!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.43,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰兇巴巴的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請...請別吵架啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.82,0:21:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.53,0:21:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.54,0:21:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.35,0:22:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.72,0:22:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.40,0:22:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.20,0:22:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.14,0:22:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.71,0:22:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.45,0:22:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.39,0:22:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.97,0:22:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好高興喔\N單獨跟英司一起出門了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.60,0:22:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺，希望您能平安歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.34,0:22:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出斗牙的假日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:23:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週 我們也將照料各位的和平!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.18,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該就叫做約會 對吧